Class Notes

  • java.lang.Object
    • Objects.Notes

  • public class Notes
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds the information around notes for the various attributes within the database, with the key being the target of the note is the SINGLE id that is not a -1 value, and that number is the key for the correct attribute to which this note is targeted to ****NOTE: This class is not yet active in the UI****
    Since:
    3/1/2021
